the type-check/build.

## Checklist (tailor to this project)
1. **Business rules** (`.claude/knowledgebase/` rules doc) — no regressions to the core invariants.
2. **Known pitfalls** (`.claude/rules/conventions.md`) — the specific traps this team hits.
3. **Edge cases** — {{timezone/rounding/locale, ordering, null/empty, concurrency}} as applicable.
4. **UX completeness** (if UI) — empty/loading/error states; feedback on mutations; navigation.
5. **Hygiene** — reused helpers (no duplication), no dead code/stray logs, type-safe, build clean.

## Output
Prioritized punch-list (Critical/High/Medium/Low): each with file:line + concrete fix. One line on what's fine.
